  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The sequel to <i>Overwords</i> is here, now with an infinite mode. Pick a word, place it on the board, and let overlapping letters fuse into new words—plan carefully and expand the board. Chase your high score for as long as you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100% free.</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minimalist, distraction-free design</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless gameplay</strong> with online high scores</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10 achievements</strong> to unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relaxing audio landscape</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No ads, no in-app purchases</strong> — pure, gameplay-first focus</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Support a passionate solo developer</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Overwords:Infinity</i> is my answer to players of the original game asking for more. Please enjoy, I hope you like it. Thanks for playing!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The sequel to <i>Overwords</i> is here, now with an infinite mode. Pick a word, place it on the board, and let overlapping letters fuse into new words—plan carefully and expand the board. Chase your high score for as long as you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100% free.</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minimalist, distraction-free design</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless gameplay</strong> with online high scores</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10 achievements</strong> to unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relaxing audio landscape</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No ads, no in-app purchases</strong> — pure, gameplay-first focus</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Support a passionate solo developer</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Overwords:Infinity</i> is my answer to players of the original game asking for more. Please enjoy, I hope you like it. Thanks for playing!</p>",
